msgid ""
"Whether through your <strong>eCommerce site</strong> or <strong>Point of "
"Sale</strong>,\n"
"            you can sell memberships that automatically grant discounts and "
"perks to your members\n"
"            and sponsors."
msgstr ""
"Uanset om det er via din <strong>webshop-</strong> eller <strong>POS-side</"
"strong>,\n"
"            så kan du sælge medlemskaber, der automatisk giver rabatter og "
"fordele til dine medlemmer\n"
"            og sponsorer."

#. module: student_organization
#: model_terms:event.event,description:student_organization.event_event_2
msgid ""
"Whether you're here to party, make memories, or just enjoy a magical night "
"out — this is your moment. Bring your friends, your best outfit, and your "
"party spirit."
msgstr ""
"Uanset om du er her for at feste, skabe minder eller bare nyde en magisk "
"aften i byen — så er dette dit øjeblik. Tag dine venner, dit bedste tøj og "
"din feststemning med."

